snippet.title: Way of the Hunter | Tikamoon Plains DLC Release Trailer
snippet.description:
The Tikamoon Plains DLC for Way of the Hunter is OUT NOW on PC, PlayStation 5, and Xbox Series X|S. 

Experience unique African environments – from lush grasslands and riverside forests in the southeast, to the arid savannahs with scattered trees and bushes, to the mountainous and desert regions in the west of Tikamoon Plains.
